Thorns kinda bad right now but can still be worth it if they have a lot of AD and casters etc, Deadman's pretty situational too but can be useful - you'll normally be choosing between maw, Mercurial, PD, GA or banshees and maybe occasionally mallet though and otherwise if you don't need them, just go straight for DPS like PD, rageblade, reaver or Deaths Dance - PD for 1v1's, Deaths Dance if they got a few bursters, rageblade if u feel like it or reaver if u just want some nifty stats and then fill build with the others, alot of the time this season you don't really need a defensive item but if they have a strong team comp or a few assassins, then mercurial, banshees or GA can be great in certain situations.
